{"tid":1382341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"保護環境－認識污水渠雨水渠","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:41:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T04:40:30.000Z","uid":88428,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6c6d1696ccf36bd8ed4aa561d9d1e7dcb58fcc92","tid":1382341,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:41:46.000Z","msg":"大家好，為保護香港環境，請認識以下基本街道渠務知識<br />\n街上的沙井渠蓋只有兩款：<br />\n一、雨水渠<br />\n入面流既係清水，雖然通常會有少量固體垃圾（eg. 樹葉、水樽、廢紙），但唔會有沼氣。<br />\n如果落完雨或瘀塞通常都係積左水係入面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyv7bJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftyv7bJL.jpg&h=b1a60e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二、污水渠<br />\n入面流既係污水（eg. 油、屎、尿），一打開既通常會有一大群小強空湧而出。<br />\n積聚左沼氣臭氣，遇高溫或火花有機會產生爆炸。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cw5V43M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCw5V43M.jpg&h=775c4334&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁有咩要注意呢？<br />\n一、渠蓋如果唔見左，係會好危險，因為個深度應該有大約一米，如果行路唔戴眼就好易差錯腳掉落去，所以要做好安全標記，提示人唔好行近。如果渠口冇圍封好，或者上面鋪左紙皮，然後有人行差踏錯掉左落去，後果會好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二、如果渠蓋唔見左，車輛就唔能夠駛過，會好影響交通<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要開渠蓋就要用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">渠匙</span>，只要左右手各拎一個，係渠蓋上扎行馬，再對入個匙孔到，正常一個人一拎就起到（半三角形）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cq2V5nf02Xs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCq2V5nf02Xs&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiidagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=0da60214\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cq2V5nf02Xs</a>"},{"pid":"c06b2e1fa087fe27e7c0f9de2b3d321dc21bb302","tid":1382341,"uid":72926,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:43:28.000Z","msg":"圓清方濁"},{"pid":"2d608387b7c0da615fd3a335e8085cf865eda24c","tid":1382341,"uid":88428,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"圓清方濁<br />\n岩呀"},{"pid":"5fcbc1a654431238734b3c546752b4e30d4b59cc","tid":1382341,"uid":1797,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔好亂黎 一陣有人發夢踢粒催淚彈落污水渠沼氣爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc28d98f3f213be15cc0e18dc31e9e0f6273b303","tid":1382341,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beba279247b34b9c3ef6a3f7be0cd18e2a8514a1","tid":1382341,"uid":26045,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5fcbc1a654431238734b3c546752b4e30d4b59cc","tid":1382341,"uid":1797,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔好亂黎 一陣有人發夢踢粒催淚彈落污水渠沼氣爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/files/column_images/905994_10153762806527506_1457540080356775149_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fcolumn_images%2F905994_10153762806527506_1457540080356775149_o.jpg&h=428200c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df0dad64c289bf19d9dcea46f656f54d79079a46","tid":1382341,"uid":88428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:51:51.000Z","msg":"得個知字<br />\n冇咩特別意思"},{"pid":"3fdc870581aafdb8144222c3063a8482d40034ff","tid":1382341,"uid":88428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fcbc1a654431238734b3c546752b4e30d4b59cc","tid":1382341,"uid":1797,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔好亂黎 一陣有人發夢踢粒催淚彈落污水渠沼氣爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:53:44.000Z","msg":"所以大家要分清楚方污圓清"},{"pid":"517e984f8d52e5db81de4d61a5f140a7757f5c97","tid":1382341,"uid":106290,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"如果有人拎走咗 車就行唔到<br />\n行唔到就會塞住 係咪咁嘅意思"},{"pid":"0a264e796de6